item.title: By: Gyan Thakuri
item.dc:creator: Gyan Thakuri
item.description: I absolutely love the Whispering Snowflake Knit Gloves! The white mix design is elegant, and the intricate knit pattern is stunning. They keep my hands toasty and add a touch of style to my winter outfits.

item.title: By: Trishna Basnet
item.dc:creator: Trishna Basnet
item.description: The Misty Marble Knit Gloves are a winter must-have! The grey mix design is chic and versatile, and the soft wool keeps my hands warm and cozy.
